   <description url="http://coloane.lip6.fr/">
      Coloane is a tool designed to model complex systems using various formalisms. 
More then a simple editor, Coloane gives you the ability to use the FrameKit platform.
Thanks to a simple UI, you can invoke a large collection of tools on your model without any efforts.
